    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, a bit punchy. But I think we need to get more specific so people really feel the stakes. Can you add a section that talks about how these progressive policies aren't just \"different ideas\" but are actually dangerous for the future of our kids and the country? Make it clear that this isn't just a debate, but a fight for survival.",
